get.description:
## Description
List all webhooks created to the store.

## Rules
- Authorization is required;
- Scope `payment/webhook/list` is required;
- Context `storeId` is required.

post.description:
## Description
Create a Webhook to pool information from the transaction's event changes, requesting the endpoint previously created linked to the store.

## Rules
- Authorization is required;
- Scope `payment/webhook/create` is required;
- Context `storeId` is required.

delete.description:
## Description
Delete a previously created Webhook by `id`.

## Rules
- Authorization is required;
- Scope `payment/webhook/delete` is required;
- Context `storeId` is required;
- `webhookId` is required.

get.description:
## Description
Get a transaction by `ref` or `id`.

## Rules
- Transaction must exists;
- Authorization is required;
- Scope `payment/transaction/read` is required;
- `accountId` context is required;
- `storeId` and `customerId` context are optional.
